Exception Meaning <code>HostLinkBaseError</code> Base class for library errors <code>HostLinkError</code> PLC returned an error code <code>HostLinkProtocolError</code> Local validation or parsing failure <code>HostLinkConnectionError</code> Connect, disconnect, socket, or timeout failure <pre><code>from hostlink.errors import (
    HostLinkConnectionError,
    HostLinkError,
    HostLinkProtocolError,
)


try:
    value = await read_typed(client, "DM100", "U")
except HostLinkProtocolError as ex:
    print(f"Protocol error: {ex}")
except HostLinkConnectionError as ex:
    print(f"Connection error: {ex}")
except HostLinkError as ex:
    print(f"PLC error: code={ex.code} response={ex.response}")
</code></pre>
